In summary, LC planar photonic devices, leveraging their unique soft-matter nature and multidimensional tunability, hold irreplaceable potential in integrated photonics. By synergistically advancing science, technology, and applications, they are poised to become a cornerstone of next-generation planar photonic platforms, driving transformative progress in optical field manipulation and accelerating the high-quality development of the global photonic information industry."}}}, "rest_id": "2060853933065810207", "source": "<a href="https://mobile.twitter.com" rel="nofollow">Twitter Web App</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "95", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

