The spacex is the future data center king and internet provider.  People don't realize how fast this will happen. The rewards will be much greater than just spacex.

Communications, networking, semiconductors, hbm memory, photonics ( both networking and eventually c p u), etc.

@grok with what elon musk had said about spacex, and it's pushing data centers into space along with connecting that to version three of starlink satellites, what sectors and what companies we'll see massive increases in business besides spacex. Base this on known facts and projected information from spacex and elon musk.

