otonDelta", "screen_name": "photondelta"}]}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNjI5MzY0NzY3MzY3NzgyNDA=", "text": "PhotonVentures is a European venture capital fund dedicated to integrated photonics, investing in companies from seed to Series A and supporting their transition from early validation to scalable businesses. As a specialized deep tech investor, the fund combines capital with direct access to a global ecosystem of foundries, designers, and system integrators via PhotonDelta.

